                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Antonio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Crescenti <expan><abbr>aed</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>flamini huic defuncto <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">ab</supplied> universo ordine Valent<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">inorum</supplied> decreta est publica lauda<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">tio et locus</supplied> sepultura<supplied reason="lost">e et</supplied> funeris im<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">pe</supplied>nsa et statua ex <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> veteranorum </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Antonio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Crescenti <lb n="3"/>filio Iulia <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Maxima mater
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tafel in mehrere Fragmente gebrochen. 2 gerahmte Inschriftfelder nebeneinander; Buchstabenhöhe bezieht sich auf das linke Feld; Buchstabenhöhe im rechten Feld: 7-5. Zwischen den beiden Inschriftfeldern sowie rechts von ihnen je eine Darstellung des Attis. Ein Teil der Inschrift ist heute verschollen. (B): Battle i Huguet: Z. 1: An[to]nio; Battle i Huguet, Beltrán, AE 1933, 5: Z. 4/5: Valenti/[norum]; Battle i Huguet: Z. 6: sepulturae [et].</p>
            </div>
